::SkarBlaise::
    He stood up and looked around in this unusual valley.  He noticed that 
there had been someone near here recently and wandered down the valley hoping 
to fight or find someone as purely evil as he is.

::Knok::
    "Owww."  He woke up and looked around thinking that he was punted farther 
than usual.  He stands up and heads south into Africa.
